item.title: About me
item.description: Welcome Hi, I’m Martyna and I’m a language nerd. I realized that reading poetry isn’t as cool as it used to be a few centuries ago and I switched to NLP. On a more serious note, I’m a linguist who journeyed into the world of Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Conversational Artificial Intelligence (CAI). I managed to dig many rabbit holes in the process so I thought I would share some of those explorations with you.
